### Admin Restaurant Management API Tests
### Use with REST Client extension or Postman

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@adminToken = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###
### 1. GET ALL RESTAURANTS (for admin)
### Returns all restaurants with owner details
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/restaurants
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###
### 2. GET SPECIFIC RESTAURANT (for admin)
### Replace RESTAURANT_ID with actual restaurant UUID
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/restaurants/RESTAURANT_ID
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###
### 3. TOGGLE RESTAURANT STATUS
### Toggles is_active field (true -> false or false -> true)
### Replace RESTAURANT_ID with actual restaurant UUID
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/restaurants/RESTAURANT_ID/toggle-status
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###
### 4. UPDATE RESTAURANT (PUT - Full Update)
### Update one or multiple fields
### Replace RESTAURANT_ID with actual restaurant UUID
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/restaurants/RESTAURANT_ID
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Restaurant Name",
  "description": "Updated description of the restaurant",
  "address": "123 New Street, Budapest, Hungary",
  "phone": "+36 1 234 5678",
  "image_url": "https://example.com/restaurant-image.jpg",
  "is_active": true
}

###
### 5. UPDATE RESTAURANT - NAME ONLY
### Example: Update only the name
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/restaurants/RESTAURANT_ID
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Restaurant Name Only"
}

###
### 6. UPDATE RESTAURANT - ADDRESS AND PHONE
### Example: Update address and phone
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/restaurants/RESTAURANT_ID
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "456 Another Avenue, Budapest",
  "phone": "+36 1 987 6543"
}

###
### 7. UPDATE RESTAURANT - DESCRIPTION
### Example: Update detailed description
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/restaurants/RESTAURANT_ID
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "This is our newly updated restaurant description with more details about our cuisine, atmosphere, and service quality."
}

###
### 8. DEACTIVATE RESTAURANT
### Set is_active to false
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/restaurants/RESTAURANT_ID
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "is_active": false
}

###
### 9. ACTIVATE RESTAURANT
### Set is_active to true
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/restaurants/RESTAURANT_ID
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "is_active": true
}

###
### 10. DELETE RESTAURANT (Soft Delete)
### Sets is_active to false (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/restaurants/RESTAURANT_ID
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

###
### 11. TEST: Admin Authorization - Missing Token
### Should return 401 error
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/restaurants
Content-Type: application/json

###
### 12. TEST: Non-Admin Access (if you have a regular user token)
### Should return 403 "Access denied"
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/restaurants
Authorization: Bearer REGULAR_USER_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

